461
1885
00:58:34,869 --> 00:58:36,376
Yo..What's up?

462
1889
00:58:36,376 --> 00:58:37,764
Are you okay?

463
1893
00:58:37,764 --> 00:58:39,201
Hello..

464
1897
00:58:39,201 --> 00:58:40,277
We meet again.

465
1901
00:58:40,277 --> 00:58:42,175
We are H.C.

466
1905
00:58:42,175 --> 00:58:43,511
H.C.??

467
1909
00:58:43,511 --> 00:58:45,105
Hospital couple.

468
1913
00:58:45,105 --> 00:58:49,080
All the patients and the nurses basically gave us that official title.

469
1917
00:58:49,936 --> 00:58:51,823
What do you think? Do we suit each other?

470
1921
00:58:52,772 --> 00:58:53,506
Joon Pyo...

471
1925
00:58:54,441 --> 00:58:56,041
Do you still not remember anything ?

472
1929
00:58:56,995 --> 00:58:58,778
