473
1933
00:58:59,179 --> 00:59:00,234
Geum Jan Di.

474
1937
00:59:00,870 --> 00:59:02,271
You don't remember?

475
1941
00:59:02,271 --> 00:59:05,066
So why do you keep talking about Jan Di or something?!

476
1945
00:59:05,066 --> 00:59:07,187
