477
1949
00:59:08,554 --> 00:59:09,989
Oh, forget it!

478
1953
00:59:10,023 --> 00:59:13,226
I don't know where you met this girl...so unsophisticated..

479
1957
00:59:13,226 --> 00:59:14,761
What does she think she is...a gang member or something?

480
1961
00:59:16,062 --> 00:59:17,864
Just make sure she doesn't come in and out of my hospital room.

481
1965
00:59:17,864 --> 00:59:19,003
Goo Joon Pyo!

482
1969
00:59:21,134 --> 00:59:22,235
Please Stop.

483
1973
00:59:44,090 --> 00:59:45,124
What is wrong with him?

484
1977
01:00:09,015 --> 01:00:09,649
Sunbae.

485
1981
01:00:22,762 --> 01:00:24,063
I'll bring tea.

486
1985
01:00:26,432 --> 01:00:27,366
I'm sorry

487
1989
01:00:33,672 --> 01:00:36,275
Why should you be sorry?

488
1993
01:00:36,275 --> 01:00:37,777
I'm the one who is sorry.

489
1997
01:00:39,063 --> 01:00:40,880
I got so mad without even my knowing...

490
2001
01:00:44,618 --> 01:00:48,011
I didn't stop you because I thought Joon Pyo would be hurt.

491
2005
01:00:48,011 --> 01:00:51,973
If you hit him, I thought you would be hurt more, emotionally.

492
2009
01:00:51,973 --> 01:00:54,937
That's why I stopped you .

493
2013
01:00:59,924 --> 01:01:02,378
How long did you wait outside?

494
2017
01:01:02,378 --> 01:01:04,994
Why are your hands so cold?

495
2021
01:01:08,164 --> 01:01:10,218
Let me see.

496
2025
01:01:15,871 --> 01:01:17,869
The one that's cold

497
2029
01:01:17,869 --> 01:01:20,154
is your heart.

498
2033
01:01:22,096 --> 01:01:25,631
You don't have to pretend to be strong in front of me.

499
2037
01:01:30,320 --> 01:01:32,558
I'm not pretending to be strong.

500
2041
01:01:34,523 --> 01:01:36,237
It's because you're here.

501
2045
01:01:37,675 --> 01:01:41,013
You being here gives me strength.

502
2049
01:01:45,560 --> 01:01:47,148
I'll go make tea.

503
2053
01:02:36,538 --> 01:02:42,619
Abracadabra,  Goo Joon Pyo, remember Geum Jan Di.

504
2057
01:02:42,619 --> 01:02:44,369
I remember.

505
2061
01:02:44,369 --> 01:02:46,380
The thing I forgot is...

506
2065
01:02:46,800 --> 01:02:51,000
you, right? 
 It's all over now.

507
2070
01:02:51,056 --> 01:02:53,177
That in this ridiculous way...

508
2074
01:02:53,177 --> 01:02:55,210
...you guys are ending....

509
2078
01:02:55,210 --> 01:02:58,449
I can't go along with it.

510
2082
01:02:58,449 --> 01:03:01,270
That girl's facial expression...I can't seem to erase...

511
2086
01:03:01,270 --> 01:03:02,198
In the end...

512
2090
01:03:02,198 --> 01:03:05,032
Geum Jan Di and Goo Joon Pyo...

513
2094
01:03:06,843 --> 01:03:08,558
only amounted to this.

514
2098
01:03:08,558 --> 01:03:10,936
This is all it amounted to..

